 multi-currency, and payment integration. Track balances and settle group dues instantly."},{title:"Educational App",callbackFnType:eu,description:"Develop a web app for interactive learning with videos, quizzes, adaptive paths, and teacher tools. Add gamification and peer discussion boards."},{title:"Corporate Wellness & Yoga App",callbackFnType:eu,description:"Build a web app for workplace wellness with yoga, mindfulness, and team challenges. Include HR metrics and wearables integration."},{title:"Crypto Trading Platform",callbackFnType:eu,description:"Create a web app for crypto trading with real-time charts, AI suggestions, staking, and KYC security. Add tutorials for beginners."},{title:"Stock Trading App",callbackFnType:eu,description:"Design a mobile app for stock trading with live quotes, alerts, and fractional investing. Offer charts, news, and goal-based tools."},{title:"Reimagine Airbnb",callbackFnType:eu,description:"Redesign Airbnb as a web app with curated stays, local experiences, and itinerary tools. Add host connections and unique filters."},{title:"Food Delivery App",callbackFnType:eu,description:"Build a mobile app for food delivery with live tracking, personalized suggestions, and loyalty perks. Manage menus and zones in real-time."},{title:"E-commerce Product Page",callbackFnType:eu,description:"Create a web page with 360° product views, reviews, and urgency cues. Optimize for engagement with sticky buttons and quick checkout."},{title:"Quick Commerce App",callbackFnType:eu,description:"Develop a mobile app for fast essentials delivery with real-time stock, voice search, and subscriptions. Optimize routes and sync inventory."}]);function em(e){let t,i,s,n,r=(0,F.c)(13),{suggestions:o,onSuggestionClick:l,title:c,className:d,variant:u}=e,p=void 0===c?"Not sure where to start? Try one of these:":c;if(!o||0===o.length)return null;let m=`flex flex-col gap-4 mt-8  ${void 0===d?"":d}`;if(r[0]!==p?(t=(0,a.jsx)(z.Text,{size:"b1",className:"font-bold text